title: THIS IS YOUR YEAR
itunes:title: THIS IS YOUR YEAR
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
THIS IS YOUR YEAR! Get ready for this... It's a powerful New Year Motivational Speech to get you ready to attack the new year! Featuring new motivational speeches from Motiversity speakers Marcus Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity), Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity) and Dr. Jessica Houston (https://bit.ly/DrJessicaHoustonMotiversity).


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), and Secession Studios (https://bit.ly/SecessionStudiosYouTube).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
